##DESCRIPTION
##  Algebra problem: Finding critical information about rational functions
##          Domain
##          Roots (2 distinct)
##          Vertical Asymptotes (1)
##          Holes (1 distinct)
##          Horizontal Asymptotes
##  All guaranteed to be found for the function
##  Leading Coefficients may not be 1
##ENDDESCRIPTION
